profile:
Inspect Tech Property Inspections uses the latest in industry equipment to accurately inspect your property. This, combined with our experience and education, makes us your #1 choice for residential and commercial inspections in Oxford, Perth, Huron, London/Middlesex, Brant, Elgin, Norfolk, Haldimand, Hamilton-Wentworth, Kitchener-Waterloo and Halton.

Inspect Tech Property Inspections provides building inspections in Southern Ontario. Inspect Tech Property Inspections is a member of the Ontario Association of Home Inspectors (OAHI), The Canadian Association of Home and Property Inspectors (CAHPI), and strictly adheres to the Code of Ethics and Standards of Practice of OAHI. Inspect Tech Property Inspections is dedicated to providing the highest level of professional service to our individual clients and the real estate industry.
 
We use an on-site computer generated inspection reporting system that is complete, comprehensive,easy-to-understand and above all legible. We provide our clients with the option of receiving a report book or soft copy of their inspection report. We use state of the art equipment that is standard with every inspection; Flir infrared cameras, REED video borascope, REED moisture meters, Nikon HD cameras, roofing pole cameras and standard electrical testing equipment. This equipment is standard with no surcharge or hidden fees.
